vote.title: An ordinance amending Ordinance No. 31400, previously approved on December 11, 2019, which abandoned portions of Fiji, Tonga and Sphinx Streets and two alleys, located near the intersection of Fran Way and Compton Streets to Fiji Property Owners Association, Inc., to extend the final replat from one year to three years - Revenue: General Fund $5,400.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
